snippet.title: Dark Card Trailer 2
snippet.description: Dark Card is a survival horror game about a boy who falls down a wish-granting well and has to find his way out. Explore the dank cave. Search for cards to help you survive. Play cards both inside and outside of battle to help fend off monsters. Find weird creatures and unspeakable horrors. Play today! https://kerly26.itch.io/dark-card
